          <dt>Context</dt>     <dd>Jesus' first extended discourse in Matthew, delivered on a hillside near Capernaum; a Galilean crowd including disciples</dd>
          <dt>Theme</dt>       <dd>The ethics and interior life of the Kingdom of God — who belongs, how they live, and what they hope for</dd>
